2%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20turned%20a%20chicken%20coop%20into%20a%20two-bedroom%20Airbnb.%20It%20makes%20over%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20and%20covers%20my%20mortgage%20payment.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20left%2C%20an%20old%2C%20dilapidated%20barn%2C%20and%20on%20the%20right%2C%20an%20updated%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681bcb8da466d2b74ab5559c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELandon%20Wilkinson%20turned%20an%20old%20chicken%20coop%20on%20his%20property%20into%20a%20successful%20Airbnb%20rental.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Landon%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20homeowner%20in%20Washington%20state%20turned%20a%20dilapidated%20chicken%20coop%20into%20a%20successful%20Airbnb%20rental.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20it%20cost%20about%20%2438%2C000%20to%20renovate%20the%20coop%2C%20which%20now%20brings%20in%20more%20than%20%242%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20started%20out%20as%20a%20shed%20used%20for%20personal%20projects%20is%20now%20a%20reliable%20way%20to%20cover%20his%20mortgage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20conversations%20with%20Landon%20Wilkinson%2C%20an%20Airbnb%20host%20in%20Yakima%2C%20Washington%2C%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20southeast%20of%20Seattle.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20two%20rentals%20on%20the%20Washington%20property%20%E2%80%94%20a%20converted%20chicken%20coop%2C%20with%20rates%20from%20around%20%24120%20a%20night%20and%20up%2C%20and%20a%20shipping%20container%20%E2%80%94and%20a%20third%20in%20Montana.%20The%20conversations%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20an%20Airbnb%20host%20for%20going%20on%2010%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Airbnb%20really%20became%20a%20thing%2C%20I%20did%20some%20couch-surfing.%20That%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20precursor%20to%20Airbnb%20and%20a%20really%20fun%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%20own%20travels%2C%20I%20got%20a%20taste%20for%20what%20was%20possible%20when%20people%20opened%20up%20their%20own%20homes%20and%20did%20cool%20things.%20When%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20I%20had%20a%20construction%20company.%20We%20fixed%20up%20houses%20and%20started%20doing%20long-term%20rentals.%20Then%2C%20around%202016%2C%20we%20attempted%20Airbnb%20with%20a%20really%20small%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20might%20have%20rented%20for%20%24900%20or%20%241%2C100%20a%20month%20as%20a%20long-term%20rental%2C%20but%20we%20were%20pretty%20routinely%20making%20%241%2C600%20to%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20as%20an%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20flipping%20houses%20for%20my%20dad%2C%20but%20the%20chicken%20coop%20was%20more%20ambitious%20than%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20previous%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20old%20barn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681ba13bc6ad288d14804a46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20state%20of%20the%20original%20chicken%20coop.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Landon%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20visualize%20something%20out%20of%20that%20building%20was%20a%20very%20organic%20process.%20It%20started%20with%20fixing%20up%20the%20roof%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20and%20putting%20in%20some%20nicer%20windows.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20just%20make%20it%20a%20little%20shop.%20I'll%20make%20it%20more%20insulated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20through%20that%20process%2C%20I%20realized%2C%20%26quot%3BActually%2C%20I%20could%20make%20something%20really%20nice%20with%20this%20if%20I%20wanted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20went%20all%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239268c05-dda4-4112-ba42-ae13f3f671b7%5C%22%3EDemolishing%20it%20would%20have%20cost%20%2420%2C000%2C%20and%20fixing%20it%20up%20was%20around%20%2438%2C000%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20the%2055-acre%20property%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%202018%20from%20my%20parents%2C%20who%20had%20bought%20it%20and%20were%20basically%20using%20it%20as%20additional%20farmland%20for%20hay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20a%20house%20on%20it%20at%20one%20point%2C%20but%20it%20had%20burned%20down.%20There%20was%20nothing%20really%20on%20the%20property%20besides%20the%20chicken%20coop%20walls%20with%20a%20sort-of%20roof%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20think%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%20anything%20with%20the%20chicken%20coop.%20It%20was%20a%20100-year-old%2C%20board-formed%20concrete%20structure.%20It%20was%20super%20dense%20and%20very%20difficult%20to%20demolish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20either%20spend%20%2420%2C000%20trying%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20this%20structure%2C%20or%20we%20could%20see%20what%20we%20could%20make%20out%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20old%20barn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681ba164a466d2b74ab54d05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20chicken%20coop%20from%20Wilkinson's%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Landon%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20landscape%20the%20property%20near%20where%20we%20had%20built%20our%20primary%20home.%20Every%20morning%2C%20we'd%20look%20out%20the%20back%20porch%20and%20see%20this%20chicken%20coop%20that%20was%20a%20real%20eyesore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20chipping%20away%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202019.%20It%20started%20to%20become%20more%20of%20a%20project%2C%20and%20I%20brought%20in%20some%20of%20my%20guys%20from%20the%20construction%20company%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20in%20%2438%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20nights%20and%20weekends%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20it%20live%20and%20set%20up%20the%20first%20time.%20Then%2C%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we've%20updated%20things%2C%20like%20furniture.%20We%20got%20a%20nicer%20hot%20tub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20home%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20renovated.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681ba18e3fe8d39283653460%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20chicken%20coop%20during%20its%20renovation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Landon%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20a%20new%20back%20window%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20paid%20just%20%2440%20for%20it.%20If%20you're%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20creative%20on%20some%20things%20or%20willing%20to%20be%20flexible%2C%20those%20can%20be%20really%20big%20finds.%20That%20window%20new%20would've%20been%20a%20couple%20grand%2C%20probably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c857376f-d180-4517-a828-3928696a3772%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thought%20th%20coop%20wouldn't%20appeal%20to%20Airbnb%20guests%2C%20but%20my%20wife%20saw%20potential%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20part%20of%20the%20story%20where%20my%20wife%20will%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20you%20tell%20them%20how%20much%20you%20resisted%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20was%20the%20one%20who%20felt%20confident%20about%20it%20being%20an%20Airbnb.%20I%20still%20had%20the%20image%20of%20a%20chicken%20coop%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20argued%20about%20it%20a%20fair%20bit.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20list%20the%20property%20photos%20of%20the%20landscape%20and%20describe%20what%20we%20can%20about%20the%20property%20and%20put%20a%20fairly%20low%20nightly%20rate%20on%20it%2C%20and%20we'll%20set%20a%20date%20when%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20updated%20chicken%20coop%20turned%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681ba1b8c6ad288d14804a5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20finished%20rental%2C%20with%20the%20main%20house%20behind%20it.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Landon%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20the%20project%20in%20December%202019%20as%20a%20shed%20for%20my%20storage.%20By%20January%2C%20we%20realized%20it%20could%20be%20more%20than%20that.%20We%20turned%20it%20into%20the%20rental%20by%20April%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20nurse%20who%20came%20in%20April%20of%202020%20and%20stayed%20there%20for%20two%20months.%20Once%20we%20got%20that%20booking%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20guess%20we%20really%20have%20to%20do%20this%20well%20and%20get%20it%20done%20on%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20nurse%20first%20moved%20in%2C%20we%20were%20still%20finishing%20up%20the%20landscaping%2C%20and%20we%20just%20barely%20got%20it%20done%20in%20time%20for%20her%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20there.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20left%2C%20everything%20was%20really%20well%20done%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20and%20the%20landscaping%20had%20matured%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20so%20we%20were%20able%20to%20get%20updated%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20nice%20branded%20sign%20on%20the%20door%20and%20on%20a%20pole%20outside%20the%20house%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BAhtanum%20Cottage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cc4fe8b-46e8-4835-9cca-e98e276669f2%5C%22%3EIncome%20from%20the%20Airbnb%20quickly%20covered%20our%20mortgage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cottage%20went%20live%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202020%20and%20started%20doing%20really%20well.%20The%2012%20or%2024%20months%20after%20were%20the%20highest%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20of%202020%2C%20we%20made%20about%20%246%2C000%20in%20one%20month%20from%20that%20house.%20That's%20a%20peak%20outlier%20scenario.%20We%20usually%20average%20%242%2C000%20to%20%243%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20revenue.%20It%20averages%20around%2065%25%20to%2070%25%20occupancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bedroom%20inside%20an%20Airbnb.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d0e673fe8d39283655981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20chicken%20coop.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Feist%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%2040-foot%2C%20high-cube%20shipping%20container%20that%20I%20used%20when%20we%20stopped%20using%20the%20chicken%20coop%20for%20storage%2C%20to%20put%20our%20lawn%20and%20garden%20stuff.%20After%20the%20coop%20cottage%20was%20built%2C%20I%20started%20to%20envision%20what%20might%20work%20with%20the%20shipping%20container.%20So%20we%20embarked%20on%20building%20that%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Airbnb%20listings%20are%20more%20than%20covering%20our%20mortgage%2C%20which%20is%20around%20%241%2C100%20a%20month.%20Our%20utilities%20in%20Washington%2C%20with%20three%20properties%20and%20two%20hot%20tubs%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20somewhere%20between%20%24400%20to%20%24500%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228093dc06-4985-42aa-a9cd-76c71e79f959%5C%22%3EIt's%20harder%20to%20start%20an%20Airbnb%20these%20days%2C%20but%20the%20potential%20for%20profit%20is%20bigger%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20work%20to%20get%20an%20Airbnb%20set%20up%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20now%20that%20the%20competition%20is%20stiffer.%20In%20the%20early%20days%2C%20it%20was%20pretty%20easy%20to%20make%20something%20work%20on%20Airbnb.%20Now%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20competitive%20in%20adding%20amenities%20that%20really%20sell%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hot%20tub%20on%20an%20Airbnb%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d0e2da466d2b74ab5720f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Feist%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20able%20to%20manage%20a%20property%20well%2C%20Airbnb%20is%20generally%20a%20much%20better%20return%20on%20investment%20than%20a%20long-term%20rental.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20you%20can't%20make%20long-term%20rentals%20work%20at%20the%20current%20mortgage%20rates%20anyway.%20So%2C%20unless%20you%20got%20in%20while%20rates%20were%20still%20low%2C%20you're%20kind%20of%20forced%20to%20be%20somewhat%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken%20coop%20started%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20get%20rid%20of%20this%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%2C%20when%20we%20were%20looking%20at%20it%20in%20its%20former%20state%2C%20to%20visualize%20it%20as%20anything%20else.%20But%20once%20you%20start%20to%20fix%20up%20a%20few%20little%20things%2C%20the%20vision%20becomes%20clearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20probably%20could've%20marketed%20it%20as%20a%20chicken%20coop%2C%20but%20it's%20one%20of%20those%20things%20that%2C%20to%20me%2C%20seemed%20like%20it%20could%20backfire.%20We%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20something%20that%20people%20perceived%20as%20what%20it%20is%20now%20instead%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20man%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dump%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20probably%20would%20have%20been%20a%20great%20marketing%20move%2C%20but%20I%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20chicken%2C%20no%20pun%20intended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20we%20weren't%20as%20confident%20that%20a%20unique%20stay%2C%20being%20a%20chicken%20coop%2C%20would've%20been%20a%20positive%20thing.%20Now%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20it%20probably%20would've%20been%20a%20good%20idea.%3C%2Fp%