20spilled%20into%20financial%20markets%2C%20whose%20swings%20have%20at%20times%20been%20like%20a%20check%20engine%20light%20for%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20labor%20market%20that's%20%26quot%3Bparalyzed%2C%26quot%3B%20Cory%20Stahle%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20the%20Indeed%20Hiring%20Lab%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmployers%20are%20not%20sure%20if%20they%20can%20commit%20to%20certain%20hiring%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20if%20you're%20thinking%20about%20handing%20in%20your%20two%20weeks'%20notice%2C%20you%20likely%20have%20more%20to%20consider%20than%20only%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20including%20how%20robust%20your%20network%20is%2C%20how%20many%20job%20postings%20there%20are%20in%20your%20field%2C%20and%20how%20well%20your%20employer%20is%20doing%2C%20Susan%20Peppercorn%2C%20an%20executive%20coach%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20the%20strongest%20job%20market%2C%20but%20then%20again%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20weakest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20job%20postings%20in%20the%20US%20have%20dropped%20by%205%20percentage%20points%20in%202025%2C%20Stahle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207298577-4e2e-4f69-9443-125460f24411%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20the%20same%20job%20market%20it%20was%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPostings%20for%20white-collar%20roles%20fell%20by%2012.7%25%20from%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%20to%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20according%20to%20Revelio%20Labs%2C%20which%20examines%20employment%20trends.%20In%20the%20same%20period%2C%20openings%20for%20blue-collar%20jobs%20dropped%20by%2011.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20longer%20view%2C%20opportunities%20for%20some%20desk%20jobs%20are%20far%20less%20prevalent%20than%20during%20the%20job-hopping%20bonanza%20of%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20From%20the%20Great%20Resignation%20era%20in%20early%202022%20through%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20po