0StepStone%20came%20to%20the%20firm%20for%20a%20change%20of%20pace%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20recent%20junior%20hires%20appreciate%20that%20every%20day%20can%20be%20different%3A%20different%20sponsors%2C%20different%20sectors%2C%20and%20different%20companies%2C%20with%20many%20active%20deals%20at%20all%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Roche%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolly%20McCarthy%2C%20founder%20of%20Opus%20Advisors%2C%20compared%20the%20workload%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsample%20platter%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bsizes%2C%20sectors%2C%20and%20strategies.%26quot%3B%26quot%3BYou%20can%20work%20on%20a%20tech%20venture%20deal%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20a%20megafund%20buyout%20deal%20by%20lunch%2C%20and%20a%20real%20estate%20deal%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%26quot%3B%20McCarthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22517aff21-88e1-4517-b260-1a95a281b199%5C%22%3EThe%20hours%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESecondaries%20can%20also%20offer%20a%20bit%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftime-to-rethink-what-work-life-balance-really-means-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20corporate%20buyout%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20control%20over%20your%20calendar%2C%26quot%3B%20McCarthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnors%20said%20buyouts%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20like%20%26quot%3Bbanking%202.0%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20highly%20demanding%2C%20intense%20workload.%20Secondaries%20offer%20more%20%26quot%3Bpredictability%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20though%20the%20recent%20increase%20in%20activity%20has%20likely%20led%20to%20longer%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20pay%20is%20below%20that%20of%20a%20buyout%20fund%20star%2C%20it's%20not%20by%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20earn%20slightly%20less%2C%20but%20the%20trade-off%20in%20deal%20reps%20and%20lifestyle%20is%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20McCarthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20don't%20expect%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20always%20be%20home%20for%20dinner.%20Schedules%20can%20still%20be%20%26quot%3Binconsistent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brittain.%20%26quot%3BLike%20many%20transaction%20and%20investment-oriented%20jobs%2C%20you%20don't%20always%20have%20control%20of%20timelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22157f608a-8a8a-4947-9016-2f4afb3ea502%5C%22%3EThe%20deals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secondary%20investor%20is%20focused%20primarily%20on%20financial%20modeling%2C%20research%2C%20and%20closing%20deals.%20It's%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20underwrite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportfolio-operations-jobs-rising-stars-of-private-equity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eversus%20meeting%20with%20CEOs%20and%20running%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrittain%20said%20secondary%20investors%20who%20buy%20a%20share%20of%20a%20fund%20must%20do%20financial%20due%20diligence%20on%20the%20overall%20fund%2C%20including%20the%20deals%20in%20the%20fund%20and%20the%20private%20equity%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20GP-led%20side%2C%20diligence%20is%20even%20more%20thorough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20underwriting%2020%20assets%20or%20200%20assets%2C%20you're%20underwriting%20one%20or%20a%20small%20number%20of%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20look%20under%20the%20hood%20of%20other%20private%20equity%20firms.%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20underwrite%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20GP%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittain%20said.%20%26quot%3BCan%20they%20buy%20well%3F%20Can%20they%20exit%20well%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-secondaries-top-firms-careers-workflow-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746777661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681a4d8aa466d2b74ab52fd7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%2