0into%20a%20bicycle%20margin%2C%20then%20you%20might%20as%20well%20get%20ready%20to%20have%20your%20exit%20strategy%20for%20your%20business%20because%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20Fisher%2C%20who%20owns%20several%20bike%20shops%20in%20Nevada%20and%20Utah%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Fisher%20decided%20to%20be%20transparent%20with%20his%20customers%20about%20why%20prices%20were%20rising%20on%20some%20of%20his%20products.%20He%20added%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frepublican-business-owner-tariff-tax-line-item-price-tags-transparency-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20line%20item%3C%2Fa%3E%20directly%20to%20the%20price%20tags%20on%20bikes%20hanging%20in%20his%20shops.%20On%20one%20bike%20he%20sells%20for%20%247%2C999%2C%20the%20price%20tag%20now%20shows%20an%20additional%20%24300%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20Tariff%20Charge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20problem%20labeling%20where%20this%20tax%20is%20coming%20from%20on%20my%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20need%20to%20know%20that%20so%20I%20have%20a%20fighting%20chance%20on%20my%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20imposed%20a%2010%25%20baseline%20tariff%20on%20all%20imports%20into%20the%20US%2C%20as%20well%20as%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20dozens%20of%20trading%20partners.%20Though%20some%20of%20the%20higher%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20those%20on%20China%20and%20some%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20%E2%80%94%20are%20on%20pause%2C%20the%20sweeping%2010%25%20tariffs%20are%20still%20in%20place.%20And%20prices%20are%20starting%20to%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmain-street-trump-trade-war-tariffs-small-businesses-impact-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrick-and-mortar%20retailers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20online%20small%20businesses%2C%20many%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20tariffs%20are%20forcing%20them%20to%20pass%20the%20cost%20to%20consumers%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20because%20they%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%20for%20smaller%20operations%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20same%20bargaining%20power%20with%20suppliers%20or%20cash%20flow%20as%20larger%20retailers%20like%20Walmart.%20Suppliers%20in%20some%20manufacturing%20hubs%20like%20China%20are%20also%20seeing%20ever%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-companies-china-suppliers-cut-prices-trump-tariff-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E-shrinking%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-companies-china-suppliers-cut-prices-trump-tariff-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20margins%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20absorb%20the%20tariff%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmall%20businesses%20are%20basically%20in%20danger%20of%20going%20out%20of%20business%20because%20of%20these%20high%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Peter%20Cohan%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20management%20at%20Babson%20College%20and%20a%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they're%20trying%20to%20preserve%20the%20trust%20of%20their%20customers%20by%20being%20very%20transparent%20about%20why%20they're%20raising%20the%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20they're%20going%20to%20lose%20customers%20because%20of%20the%20higher%20rates%2C%20but%20at%20least%20being%20transparent%20will%20help%20reduce%20the%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-effects-retailers-consumer-brands-hasbro-coca-cola-amazon-adidas-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarger%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20also%20have%20considered%20such%20transparency%20measures.%20After%20reports%20that%20Amazon%20is%20going%20to%20start%20displaying%20how%20much%20tariffs%20are%20contributing%20to%20the%20price%20of%20goods%20on%20its%20platform%2C%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaroline-leavitt-white-house-press-secretary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20idea%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-tariff-costs-trump-schumer-mtg-response-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehostile%20and%20political%20act%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20The%20e-commerce%20giant%20denied%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20display%20the%20cost%20of%20tariffs%2C%20saying%20its%20low-price%20section%2C%20Haul%2C%20had%20considered%20it%20for%20some%20items%20but%20then%20jettisoned%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20fast-fashion%20giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-order-delivery-after-trump-tariffs-extra-fees-explained-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShein%20and%20Temu%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20145%25%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%20the%20canceled%20de%20minimus%20exemptions%20%E2%80%94%20posted%20identical%20customer%20notices%20on%20their%20websites%2C%20saying%20that%20that%20there%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bprice%20adjustments%26quot%3B%20because%20their%20%26quot%3Boperating%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%26quot%3B%20under%20%26quot%3Brecent%20changes%20in%20global%20trade%20rules%20and%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20Temu%20started%20adding%20%26quot%3Bimport%20charges%26quot%3B%20at%20checkout%2C%20which%20can%20double%20the%20price%20of%20the%20item.%20By%20May%2C%20Temu's%20main%20website%20appeared%20to%20have%20blocked%20US%20customers%20from%20seeing%20products%20shipped%20from%20China%2C%20and%20the%20site%20is%20filled%20with%20products%20marked%20%26quot%3Blocal%26quot%3B%20to%20signify%20they%20are%20at%20a%20warehouse