Rescript%2C%20starting%20with%20recycled%20copier%20paper%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20novelty%20does%20not%20always%20translate%20to%20repeat%20business.%20The%20duo%20realised%20that%20plantable%20stationery%20was%20treated%20as%20a%20one-time%20gift.%20Even%20though%20it%20was%20impressive%2C%20companies%20were%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20one-time%20buy.%20To%20build%20a%20sustainable%20business%20that%20has%20a%20greater%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20offer%20something%20people%20used%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20moment%20of%20clarity%20arrived%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20While%20offices%20across%20the%20country%20were%20closed%2C%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20were%20busier%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20they%20needed%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20most%20saw%20scrap%2C%20they%20saw%20an%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20when%20we%20got%20the%20idea%20of%20selling%20copier%20paper.%20Paper%20is%20something%20we%20use%20every%20single%20day%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20recycled%20up%20to%20six%20or%20seven%20times%2C%20yet%20most%20of%20it%20still%20ends%20up%20as%20waste.%20So%20we%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20turn%20that%20missed%20opportunity%20into%20something%20meaningful%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ashutosh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20formally%20launched%20Rescript%2C%20starting%20with%20recycled%20copier%20paper.%20It%20may%20not%20have%20had%20the%20glamour%20of%20plantable%20gifts%2C%20but%20it%20had%20consistency%20and%20volume.%20Soon%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348979%2Fcotton-waste-from-factories-sustainable-stationery-rashi-agarwal-roohani-rang-recycled-diary-notebooks-support-artisans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpanded%20into%20notebooks%2C%20journals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pens%2C%20and%20pencils%2C%20creating%20a%20full%20suite%20of%20sustainable%20stationery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cornerstone%20of%20their%20innovation%20is%20a%20proprietary%20formulation%2C%20an%20industry-first%20approach%20that%20finely%20mixes%20the%20ratio%20of%20recycled%20paper%20to%20water%20during%20production.%20This%20careful%20balance%20guarantees%20the%20resulting%20paper%20is%20smooth%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20fully%20compatible%20with%20modern%20printers%2C%20addressing%20long-standing%20issues%20of%20roughness%20and%20equipment%20wear%20that%20once%20hindered%20the%20use%20of%20recycled%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescript%20uses%20recycled%20paper%20to%20make%20stationery%20items%20like%20notebooks%20and%20journals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-61_11zon-1746717946-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERescript%20uses%20recycled%20paper%20to%20make%20stationery%20items%20like%20notebooks%20and%20journals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlder%20recycled%20paper%20was%20rough%2C%20fibrous%2C%20and%20it%20used%20to%20damage%20printers.%20We%20solved%20that%20by%20designing%20a%20blend%20that%20is%20durable%20and%20safe%20for%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Naren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPaper-making%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20process%20begins%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20waste%20paper%2C%20sourced%20primarily%20from%20packaging%20trimmings%2C%20textbook%20off-cuts%2C%20and%20even%20old%20student%20notebooks.%20This%20material%20is%20sent%20to%20an%20industrial%20mill%20they%20have%20partnered%20with%20under%20a%20contract%20manufacturing%20model.%20They%20do%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20capacity%20for%20full-scale%20industrial%20papermaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20mill%2C%20the%20waste%20is%20segregated%2C%20then%20fed%20into%20a%20pulping%20machine%20that%20adds%20water%20and%20mixes%20the%20material%20into%20a%20fine%20paste.%20This%20pulp%20is%20flattened%20on%20a%20conveyor%2C%20pressed%2C%20and%20dried%20using%20heat%20to%20produce%20massive%20rolls%20of%20recycled%20paper%2C%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20reels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reels%20are%20cut%20into%20A4%2C%20A3%2C%20and%20A5%20sizes%20for%20copier%20paper%20or%20sent%20for%20ruling%20and%20printing%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20notebooks%20and%20journals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20no%20bright%20white%20papers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20bleaching%20agents%20at%20all%2C%20which%20is%20why%20our%20paper%20is%20not%20bright%20white.%20At%20first%2C%20people%20questioned%20it.%20But%20now%2C%20they%20associate%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindi