0to%20make%20a%20160-page%20notebook%2C%20workers%20sort%20and%20layer%20the%20required%20number%20of%20sheets%2C%20placing%20separators%20in%20between.%20These%20stacks%20are%20then%20placed%20into%20a%20chain-link%20machine%2C%20along%20with%20the%20notebook%20cover%2C%20where%20the%20pages%20are%20pinned%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notebooks%20then%20move%20on%20to%20a%20squaring%20machine%2C%20which%20flattens%20and%20aligns%20the%20edges.%20After%20that%2C%20they%20are%20sent%20to%20a%20cutting%20machine%20to%20give%20the%20notebook%20a%20neat%20and%20finished%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournals%20follow%20a%20slightly%20different%20process.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20ruling%2C%20the%20pages%20are%20stitched%20rather%20than%20pinned%2C%20and%20then%20taken%20to%20a%20perfect%20binding%20machine.%20This%20machine%20uses%20hot%20glue%20to%20bind%20the%20stitched%20pages%20to%20a%20sturdy%20cover%2C%20giving%20the%20journal%20both%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341205%2Fbamboo-furniture-gujarat-professor-patented-chair-sustainable-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20and%20durability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20co-founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-08T191619.872_11zon-1746712005.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20notebooks%20move%20on%20to%20a%20squaring%20machine%2C%20which%20flattens%20and%20aligns%20the%20edges%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-08T191619.872_11zon-1746712005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBl